title: Flyout using an Easyjet livery from Luton Airport (EGGW)
description:
In this video we will look at the Luton airport which is now available in the MSFS marketplace. Luton is one of the airports where you will see a lot of Easyjet aircrafts. While reviewing the images released this can be clearly seen but besides that there are also several other nice graphics which makes this addon a candy on the pie.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
